Test case 1:
LoginWithValidAccount

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
4) Into "Password" field enter value "909090"
5) Click on "Вход" button

Expected result:
User successfully logged in. User icon and login are displayed in the right-top corner.

Test case 2:
CheckThatUserCannotLogInWithoutPassword

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
4) Click on "Вход" button

Expected result:
User stayed on logIn page

Test case 3:
CheckLogout

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
4) Into "Password" field enter value "909090"
5) Click on "Вход" button
6) Click on icon in the right-top corner
7) Click on "Выход" button

Expected result:
User is logout and redirect to login page

Test case 4:
CheckResetPassword

1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Click on "Напомнить пароль" link

Expected result:
User is redirected to empty page

Test case 5:
CheckCreationOfService

Pre-conditions:
1) Open FireFox browser
2) Open web page with URL "http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login"
3) Into "Email" field enter value "Student"
3) Into "Password" field enter value "909090"
4) Click on "Вход" button
5) In sidebar-menu click on "Обслужывание"
6) Check that in table "Список работ" isn't created record with "Проведенные изменения" - "777", "Проведенные операции" - "Service operations", "Сотрудник" - "Tad Jones Brian" and "Дата" - "10.07.2015 00:00"

Steps:
7) Click on "+" button
8) Into "Service changes" field enter value "777"
9) Into "Service operations" field enter value "Service operation"
10) From "Service date" select date&time "10.07.2015 00:00"
11) From "Аппарат" combobox select value "Сломан датчик"
12) From "Сотрудник" combobox select value "Tad Jones Brian"
13) Click on "Создать" button

Post-conditions:
14) Click on record with "Проведенные изменения" - "777", "Проведенные операции" - "Service operations", "Сотрудник" - "Tad Jones Brian" and "Дата" - "10.07.2015 00:00"
15) Click on "Удалить" button

Expected result:
Record with "Проведенные изменения" - "777",
            "Проведенные операции" - "Service operations",
            "Сотрудник" - "Tad Jones Brian"
            "Дата" - "10.07.2015 00:00" is created and appears in "Список работ" table
